high_descs: Turn to the left, go forward then hang a right, go forward to the end of the counter, turn to the right to face the counter
Pick up the butter knife that is to the left of the lettuce.
Turn to the right, go forward, turn to the left to the lettuce on the counter to the left of the teapot.
Use the knife to cut the lettuce into slices.
Turn to the right, go forward to the counter, turn to the left, go to the sink ahead on the right.
Put the knife in to the sink in front of the vase.
Turn to the right, go forward to the counter, turn to the right, go forward to the end of the counter and turn right to face the sliced lettuce.
Pick up a slice of the lettuce from the counter.
Turn to the right, go forward to the fridge that is on the left.
Put the lettuce inside the fridge and close the door, remove the cold lettuce from the fridge and close the door.
Turn to the left, go to the counter, turn to the left and go to the sink ahead on the right.
Put the lettuce in the sink on the left side of the butter knife.
anns.task_desc: Put cold lettuce in a sink.

high_descs: Walk straight ahead, then turn to your right at the end of the counter.
Pick up the butter knife to the left of the head of lettuce, on the counter.
Move over to your right so that you are directly in front of the head of lettuce on the counter top.
Cut the head of lettuce, on the counter into slices.
Turn to your right and walk to the end of the counter then turn left, then go to the sink on your left.
Place the knife in the sink, in front of the bowl and the apple.
Turn to your right and go to the end of the counter, then make a right and go back to the head of lettuce, at the end of the counter, on your right.
Pick up one of the slices of lettuce on the counter.
Turn to your right and go to the refrigerator on your left.
Place the slice of lettuce in the refrigerator, on the third shelf, to the left of the tomato, wait for it to chill, then remove the slice of lettuce from the refrigerator.
Turn to your left and go back to the sink on your right.
Place the slice of lettuce in the front of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of lettuce in the sink.

high_descs: Walk to the left of the table and turn right to face the table.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Step to the right to face the lettuce on the table.
Cut the lettuce on the table into slices.
Turn right walk across the room to face the sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Turn around and walk around to face the lettuce on the table.
Pick up a slice of lettuce on the table.
Turn around and face the fridge.
cool the slice of lettuce on the shelf beside the tomato.
Turn left and walk over to face the sink.
Place the slice of lettuce on the left side of the sink.
anns.task_desc: To cool a slice of lettuce and place it in the sink.
